      "id": "step-3-access-redis-instance"
    }}>{`Step 3. Access Redis Instance`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{` redis-cli -c -p 30001
 127.0.0.1:30001> set foo bar
 -> Redirected to slot [12182] located at 127.0.0.1:30003
 OK
 127.0.0.1:30003>
`}</code></pre>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "step-4-verify-the-cluster-nodes"
    }}>{`Step 4. Verify the cluster nodes`}</h2>
